ndefined or infinity . <br />\n條題目都同你講左tan x = sin x / cos x  <br />\n咁tan 90 =  sin90 / cos 90 <br />\nTan 90 = 1/0 <br />\nLHS: undefinded or infinity <br />\nRHS: undefinded or infinity <br />\n我覺得無野可以discuss 同無咩大問題 <br />\n你自己覺得有d咩問題一齊傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先, infinity or undefined不是數字，因此不可以話：因為LHS同RHS都係undefined,所以兩者就係等於或者一樣<br />\n<br />\n我估問題的重點應該要係 tan x = sin x / cos x  對於什麼x才成立?"},{"pid":"3b57a7d179dd3394d518c48b0bf4b3f62591df9a","tid":197014,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"Sin angle sin<br />\nSin sin sin<br />\nAngle sin angle <br />\nAngel angel sin"},{"pid":"b6ff489eb50b289d8e6720c5d36cb5534fa3fa07","tid":197014,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sin angle sin<br />\nSin sin sin<br />\nAngle sin angle <br />\nAngel angel sin</blockquote><br />\nSide<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e809d34148527d46068cd191f9d2aad00d0c042","tid":197014,"uid":75103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sin angle sin<br />\nSin sin sin<br />\nAngle sin angle <br />\nAngel angel sin</blockquote><br />\nSide<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都有得笑"}]}